<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.7.1/dist/jquery.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:ital,wght@0,200..1000;1,200..1000&family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: d0d0d0;
        }

        .profilepic {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .logobawah {
            background-color: b0b8be;
        }

        .judul {
            font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .teks-testimoni {
            font-family: 'Lora', serif;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .nama {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .jabatan {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: gray;
        }
    </style>
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container py-5" style="max-width: 980;">
        <div class="bg-white p-5">
            <!--JUDUL-->
            <h2 class="text-center judul text-uppercase mb-5">Our Clients Love Us</h2>
            <!--BARIS 1 TESTIMONI-->
            <div class="row mb-4">
                <!--TESTIMONI 1-->
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-3">
                            <img src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQEeouJlc34TOQ/profile-displayphoto-scale_400_400/B56ZeLDKrSG0Ag-/0/1750384554489?e=1775088000&v=beta&t=atMfOf-awjWbI_ZlCdXJdJIVX8bxS5NMR1I2yNace3Q"
                                class="profilepic rounded-circle" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p class="teks-testimoni">Pelayanan mereka sangat memuaskan. Sejak menggunakan jasa ini, omzet bisnis saya
                                meningkat hingga dua kali lipat dalam waktu tiga bulan.</p>
                            <p class="nama">Muhammad Izzan Aquilla</p>
                            <p class="jabatan">Mahasiswa Sistem Informasi</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!--TESTIMONI 2-->
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-3">
                            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRFUTcHtAQStlvFcdvXBj6axbw7_zpsSNMsrQ&s"
                                class="profilepic rounded-circle" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p class="teks-testimoni">Saya sangat terkesan dengan kecepatan dan kualitas kerja tim mereka. Proyek selesai tepat
                                waktu dan hasilnya melebihi ekspektasi saya.</p>
                            <p class="nama">Adam Mosseri</p>
                            <p class="jabatan">CEO of Instagram</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!--BARIS 2 TESTIMONI-->
            <div class="row mb-4">
                <!--TESTIMONI 3-->
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-3">
                            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTplhMopbFLPzgR7CjuZAbv7FyN0hGzDkg2Xw&s"
                                class="profilepic rounded-circle" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p class="teks-testimoni">Platform ini benar-benar mengubah cara kerja kami. Proses yang dulu memakan waktu
                                berhari-hari kini bisa selesai dalam hitungan jam.</p>
                            <p class="nama">Mark Zuckerberg</p>
                            <p class="jabatan">CEO of Facebook</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!--TESTIMONI 4-->
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-3">
                            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"
                                class="profilepic rounded-circle" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p class="teks-testimoni">Dukungan tim support mereka luar biasa responsif. Setiap pertanyaan selalu dijawab dengan
                                cepat, jelas, dan sangat membantu.</p>
                            <p class="nama">Jeff Bezos</p>
                            <p class="jabatan">Executive Chairman of Amazon</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!--LOGO DIBAWAH-->
            <div class="logobawah py-4 mx-n5 mb-n5" style="background-color: #b0b8be; padding: 30px;">
                <div class="row text-center align-items-center">
                    <div class="col">
                        <img src="data:image/png;base64,"
                            style="height:28px;" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <img src="data:image/png;base64,"
                            style="height:28px;" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col"><img
                            src="data:image/png;base64,"
                            style="height:28px;" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col"><img
                            src="data:image/png;base64,"
                            style="height:28px;" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col"><img
                            src="data:image/png;base64,"
                            style="height:28px;" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="col"><img
                            src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABwAAAAcCAAAAABXZoBIAAAAnklEQVR4AeTNIQiDQABG4b+u17X1aF6PK3YEO9iMJqPVau82y4FgMezS0oVLhqsHtrcqeqzDXv3CEz/6L4yTtZM3dnHmPTtjzXZAXKYVo4agkU2GI2Lloc6JDez1+flswMu1EQZ3xlE7lK8eKDkjtwE+crBMV+wesKmCiisGGepZIfQJpMj9SNb2MYWrChjVkULuCyCfRvsdmBieyQQAsoDk/9ryhFMAAAAASUVORK5CYII="
                            style="height:28px;" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
